id=nothing-widevine
name=Nothing Widevine L1 enabler
version=v0.0.1
versionCode=1
author=Ubuntuify
description=Custom ROMs often disable widevine due to a non-working TEE. However, the TEE can be reprovisioned to get a key for Widevine, fixing this issue. This simply adds back the required libraries to do so.
